Jahi Amadi HASANATI, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Jason WOOD, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0361 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 9, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed as duplicative of the relief sought in case number 2D17-3642. Appellees' motion to strike and appellant's motion for extension of time to serve the initial brief are denied as moot.

SILBERMAN, VILLANTI, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
